						               													<description>You'll need to roll the dice for sets and runs for the chance to move your pawns and go for the win...will you take chances, will you play it safe, do you feel like you can get some momentum and go for that big streak!?!? No score pad, no pencils! Have a strategy, weigh the risks and hope for a little luck!!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Momentum is the STRATEGIC DICE GAME where you choose your roll type, FOCUS (best of three rolls) or MOMENTUM (unlimited amount of single rolls until you can't move) and try to be the first to move your four pawns to the center using SETS and RUNS of the dice to advance your PAWNS. The first with their four in the center wins!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Time to warm up those dice and and see if you can get some MOMENTUM!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
